  "description": "A gentle, playful preset designed for accessibility — the kalimba floor model produces warm melodic taps, the understory is clean (no bit-crush, no tape degradation), and the canopy breathes softly overhead. Bird trill creatures trigger from floor accents at low level, adding a cheerful scatter. Every note feels like a small animal discovering something delightful.",
